OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspreading northeast. Then rain
OL,8,Fovernight before drier weather spreads
OL,9,Fto all but the far east later. Fresh
OL,10,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FRain in the east soon
OL,13,Fclearing. Then sunny spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers, occasionally heavy
OL,15,Fby afternoon. Blustery southwesterly
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,19,Fcloudy with a chance of showers on
OL,20,FSaturday. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,21,FSunday and Monday.
